{
  "stem": "24466.7",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I start to look after him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And what I find?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Instead to find him, I find a shed, a colossal shed, about 20 meters long, and about [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] two and 1/2 meters high, full of tombs-- tombs-- Tombstones.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Tomb-- tombstones [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from the cemetery, one after the other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Full.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mind you, I want to tell you, it wasn't done through the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was done through the Poles, through the municipality of Poles and through the Poles, through the people and Poles what are living next to the--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the first day-- I'm coming back to it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first day when I came to Radom, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I have in mind a visit to my mother's tombs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was walking, and everything was, for me, you know, very-- I was very upset and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And walking on the [NON-ENGLISH], and a [NON-ENGLISH], a policeman, a Jewish boy-- he wasn't looking Jewish at all, with the the lea-- with the arm band, the red one.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He came to me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, I know you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You are Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Kaufman's son.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was burying your father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I asked him, that was for me?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just imagine how that-- you can imagine what-- what-- what-- what kind of a feeling I got and so I asked him, please tell me-- you are telling me something.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was burying not only your father, but other-- that was 18 people that was on the third-- the second or the third-- third May, that he was burying him.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he told me that was [INAUDIBLE], a place not far from Radom.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
